<h1>About</h1>
<p>PhlartMap provides a map display of former and current Public Art displays around Philadelphia. Our interface integrates an API of a Philadelphia Public Art index curated and developed by <a href="https://www.philart.net/chrispurdom/">Christopher William Purdom</a> on <a href="https://philart.net">philart.net</a></p>
<h2>Why is public art important?</h2>
<p>If you need to ask this question then this site is not for you.</p> 
